# ── AI Provider API Keys ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# You need at least one of these to run the app.
# The UI lets users pick which provider to use at analysis time.

# Anthropic Claude (Haiku model)
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI GPT-4o mini
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google Gemini 2.5 Flash (generous free tier, no credit card required)
# Get your key at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
